data.description: Brand New Roof.  Beautiful remodeled 3 Bedroom home nestled in the coveted community of Villas Del Mar. The property has a wonderfully large open floor plan with fantastic natural light. High quality upgrades throughout, including remodeled kitchen with stainless steel appliances, custom backsplash and beautiful stone tops. The Master Suite features a double vanity, glass enclosed shower and a separate tub. Upgraded wood floors and tile throughout. No membership required. Beautiful community pool for your enjoyment. Basic cable and lawn care are included in the HOA fees. Centrally located in an excellent A-rated school zone and conveniently located near shopping, dining and places of worship. This home is a must see!
